raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '1.1-1' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-goric
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/goric_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/goric/goric_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: f6c29913fdc4aed5f9d7b9522da7ebe53db2d632867f96fdff82c101f5630f33

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  noarch: generic
  number: 0
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:

  host:
    - r-base
    - r-mass
    - r-matrix
    - r-mvtnorm
    - r-nlme
    - r-quadprog
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-mass
    - r-matrix
    - r-mvtnorm
    - r-nlme
    - r-quadprog

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('goric')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('goric')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=goric
  license: GPL-2.0-or-later
  summary: Generalized Order-Restricted Information Criterion (GORIC) value for a set of hypotheses
    in multivariate linear models and generalised linear models.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
